---
// PremiumAboutAna.astro — Cinematic about section for Ana
---

<section id="sobre-ana" aria-labelledby="about-ana-title" class="about-section section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-wrapper" data-gsap="about">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <!-- Image column -->
        <div class="about-image-col">
          <div class="about-image-frame">
            <img
              src="/images/ana-foto.webp"
              alt="Ana, creadora del M&eacute;todo Livianas"
              width="480"
              height="600"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
              class="about-image"
              onerror="this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex';"
            />
            <!-- Fallback placeholder if image fails -->
            <div class="about-image-placeholder">
              <svg width="56" height="56" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
                <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="about-placeholder-text">Foto de Ana</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Text column -->
        <div class="about-text-col">
          <span class="about-label">SOBRE ANA</span>

          <blockquote class="about-quote">
            &ldquo;No necesit&aacute;s m&aacute;s fuerza de voluntad. Necesit&aacute;s entender por qu&eacute; hac&eacute;s lo que hac&eacute;s.&rdquo;
          </blockquote>

          <p class="about-bio">
            Ana es coach de bienestar y creadora del M&eacute;todo Livianas. Acompa&ntilde;a a mujeres a transformar su relaci&oacute;n con la comida y el cuerpo desde un enfoque integral: conducta, emoci&oacute;n y espiritualidad.
          </p>

          <div class="about-detail">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" class="about-detail-icon">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
              <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Grupos de m&aacute;ximo 8 mujeres &middot; Acompa&ntilde;amiento personalizado</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    background: var(--color-cream);
  }

  /* --- Wrapper with large radius --- */
  .about-wrapper {
    background: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-3xl);
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: var(--space-6);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about-wrapper {
      padding: var(--space-10);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .about-wrapper {
      padding: var(--space-12);
    }
  }

  /* --- Grid --- */
  .about-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 5fr 7fr;
      gap: var(--space-10);
      align-items: center;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .about-grid {
      gap: var(--space-16);
    }
  }

  /* --- Image column --- */
  .about-image-col {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .about-image-frame {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 380px;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 3px solid var(--color-moss);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-cream), var(--color-cream-warm));
    position: relative;
  }

  .about-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .about-image-placeholder {
    display: none;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    color: var(--color-moss);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-cream), var(--color-cream-warm));
  }

  .about-placeholder-text {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  /* --- Text column --- */
  .about-text-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  /* Label */
  .about-label {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-moss);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  /* Quote */
  .about-quote {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    color: var(--color-carbon);
    line-height: 1.35;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-6) 0;
    padding: 0;
    border: none;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about-quote {
      font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .about-quote {
      font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    }
  }

  /* Bio */
  .about-bio {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about-bio {
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
    }
  }

  /* Detail line */
  .about-detail {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-moss);
    font-weight: 500;
    background: var(--color-cream);
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .about-detail-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }
</style>
